---
title: Double Cherry-Glazed Smokey Chicken with Cheesy Potato Mash & Supergreen Slaw
description: BBQ chicken with a cheesy potato side and a fresh, crunchy slaw? We say yes please! This chicken is extra special, coated in a sweet cherry glaze that caramelises in the pan. You’ll be asking for seconds before you even finish your plate!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/66878b72dea0224ab073353c-5c884075.jpeg
